Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
